-pine\/\">Bristlecone Pine<\/a><br \/>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\" nofocus\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" src=\"https:\/\/th.bing.com\/th\/id\/R.22d340a10441fa671e85155124017d82?rik=k4IDVvbn4BfwGw&amp;riu=http%3a%2f%2fwww.oceanlight.com%2fstock-photo%2fpinus-longaeva-bristlecone-pine-photograph-17475-113050.jpg&amp;ehk=WxgVEj8iUmdLLIiWiJeRcvIDA5KVGw0mehy77%2fs86t4%3d&amp;risl=&amp;pid=ImgRaw&amp;r=0\" alt=\"Ancient Bristlecone Pine Trees, Pinus longaeva, White Mountains, Inyo ...\" width=\"621\" height=\"412\" aria-label=\"Ancient Bristlecone Pine Trees, Pinus longaeva, White Mountains, Inyo ...\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>YOSEMITE National Park.<br \/>\nVernal Falls\u2192Nevada Falls\u2192climb Half Dome<\/strong><br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"nofocus alignleft\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" src=\"https:\/\/preview.redd.it\/3sx94eiqceh31.jpg?auto=webp&amp;s=2ec7c7b1a7d61724a88e7b75aa02444fd2320608\" alt=\"Nevada Falls, Yosemite Valley [OC] [1080x1920] : r\/EarthPorn\" width=\"466\" height=\"622\" aria-label=\"Nevada Falls, Yosemite Valley [OC] [1080x1920] : r\/EarthPorn\" data-bm=\"7\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\" nofocus\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" src=\"https:\/\/www.josephfiler.com\/images\/xl\/California-Yosemite-Bridalveil-Falls-0990.jpg\" alt=\"Yosemite Falls\" width=\"466\" height=\"699\" aria-label=\"Yosemite Falls\" data-bm=\"6\" \/><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Yosemite Falls<br \/>\n<\/strong><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\" nofocus\" tabindex=